  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a GPicView</title>

    <para>
      The <application>GPicView</application> package contains a lightweight image
viewer.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informação do Pacote</bridgehead>
